wiki.summary: “Anxiety” is an unreleased track from Chicago native, Juice WRLD. On the Nick Mira and DT production, Juice details his anxiety and explains how he uses narcotics to control his mental state. The track was first previewed via Juice’s Twitter on December 13, 2018. The track’s instrumental was also used on TyFontaine’s November 2019 track “Pay to Play.” The track leaked in its entirety on August 15, 2020 therefore it is unknown if the track will make an official release. Read more on Last.fm.
